<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .success-box {
      background-color: #d4edda;
      border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>🔒 Email Change Request Cancelled</h2>
    <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    
    <div class="success-box">
      <strong>✅ All pending email change requests have been cancelled.</strong><br><br>
      Your account is now secure.
    </div>
    
    <p><strong>⏰ Cancelled at:</strong> {{revokeTime}}</p>
    
    <p>If you did not request this cancellation, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
    
    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">🔐 Log In to Your Account</a>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="{{supportUrl}}">{{supportUrl}}</a>.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>{{appName}} Security Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>